{"tid":1243443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"送中條例+醫管局AEIS系統漏洞 = ?","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T14:35:43.000Z","uid":37313,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b67e57aade5ecbcda8406fe682e0edae951e72cf","tid":1243443,"uid":37313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rkxC9zs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrkxC9zs.jpg&h=09dd58e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解醫管局夜晚11:00先黎發記者招待會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地驚比人問警犬點解會有後門之外<br />\n最驚係比人問送終之後加埋哩個漏洞會唔會涉及到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">器官賣買</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你仲未知醫管局個急救系統發生咩事哩度有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">陳沛然</span></span></strong>醫生既LINK片同圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPX340z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPX340z.png&h=2eac623a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最新消息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">醫管局的電腦系統和警務處的電腦系統是相連的</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/MIIDSS.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F06%2FMIIDSS.html&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=670677d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/06/MIIDSS.html</a><br />\n<br />\n好啦睇完上面篇文既你,咁我地黎睇下一個港豬全身上下係值幾多錢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAySdVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAySdVA.jpg&h=6a4e5d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港經濟日報:美媒揭器官黑巿買賣價目表 一個腎臟賣155萬港元<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2075047/%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92%E6%8F%AD%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%BF%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E5%83%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%80%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E8%85%8E%E8%87%9F%E8%B3%A3155%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2075047%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25AE%2598%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E5%2583%25B9%25E7%259B%25AE%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E3%2580%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E8%2585%258E%25E8%2587%259F%25E8%25B3%25A3155%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%2583&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=84cdf0d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2075047/%E7%BE%8E%E5%AA%92%E6%8F%AD%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E9%BB%91%E5%B7%BF%E8%B2%B7%E8%B3%A3%E5%83%B9%E7%9B%AE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%80%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E8%85%8E%E8%87%9F%E8%B3%A3155%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83</a><br />\n咁香港有七百萬人人口,事但KO一百萬人左右,都幾和味下,小熊維尼把劍又可以補幾多HP呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你可以會話,車~關我撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我無做錯野送終條例唔關我事喎<br />\n啦~你就錯啦,只要你去過急症,生仔去過急症,你同你既下一代既個人同身體資料都係個系統,如果咁岩有個高管要個腎,又有個克警又想搵下錢......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我岩岩發夢見到...<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">維基百科 : 中國器官移植</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25AE%2598%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25A4%258D&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyuxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=7763d88d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%A7%BB%E6%A4%8D</a><br />\n入面提到   <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國政府宣布，2015年1月1日起，中國宣布全面停止使用死刑罪犯器官作為供體來源。</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n但你都知終國人講既野都係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係最需要要留意既係我地既蛾蛾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKLJkJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKLJkJU.png&h=af3c0798&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢係咩撚都無做過<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果你唔想死無全屍既!<br />\n如果你唔想死後既身體都同終國共享永華既!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">快樂抗爭組</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242966/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242966/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">身體力行組</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242880/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242880/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n希望之後發夢都可以見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24567e09d8d2ed092b8b1a51f93094edc9eafef","tid":1243443,"uid":37313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae22516c94d232f35ffb4b644e76a7677788dbbf","tid":1243443,"uid":37313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:08:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e838862580243b2877a48aabb25a8ff1392687b","tid":1243443,"uid":37313,"like":0,"dislike